---
import Cases from "../components/sections/Cases.astro";
import Hero from "../components/sections/Hero.astro";
import Process from "../components/sections/Process.astro";
import Proposal from "../components/sections/Proposal.astro";
import Services from "../components/sections/Services.astro";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import LaravelCompany from "../components/sections/laravel-shopify.astro";
import Footer from "../components/ui/Footer.astro";
---

<MainLayout
        title="Laravel Development Company London"
        description="Improve your Laravel™ project with our Laravel™ agency recomandations. We offer a 48h match guarantee. 100% risk-free trial. Custom CMS, eCommerce, CRM, SaaS. Proven delivery, real results."
>
    <Hero/>

    <Process/>

    <Services/>

    <LaravelCompany/>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-screen-xl">

        <!-- Intro Paragraph -->
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Already have a brilliant idea brewing in your mind, or maybe a project that's hitting roadblocks?
            Whether you're building the next unicorn SaaS, upgrading an old dusty legacy system, or just wanna optimise
            your current <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">Laravel™</a> stack, we're
            your ride or die, fam.
        </p>

        <!-- Services Heading -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Laravel™ Services</h2>

        <!-- Services Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">

            <!-- Service Cards -->
            <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🔧</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Full Custom Laravel™ Builds</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Whether it's MVPs or Enterprise-grade portals, we deliver production-ready apps with layered
                    architecture, modular design, and TDD practices. Никакой монолитной каши. Только чистый, расширяемый
                    код.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-2">⚙️</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">API Integrations</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Connect your <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">Laravel™</a>
                    backend with third-party services like Stripe, PayPal, Twilio, Firebase, AWS, and beyond. Need
                    custom webhooks, OAuth2 integrations, or event-driven microservices? It's our playground. 😎
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🚀</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Performance Optimization</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Who wants a slow website? No one. Мы оптимизируем SQL запросы, настраиваем Redis, Horizon, и строим
                    асинхронные очереди для мгновенной обработки данных.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🛡️</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Security Hardening</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">Laravel™</a> security is 🔥 out
                    of the box, but layered security? Even better. 从CSRF保护到API加密，我们让你的应用坚不可摧。
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🎯</span>
                    <h3 title="Laravel™ consulting" class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Strategic Consulting</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Tech debt, bad architecture, slow releases? If your <a href="https://laravelcompany.com"
                                                                           class="text-blue-600 underline">Laravel™</a>
                    app’s growth is stuck, we provide detailed roadmaps, hands-on code reviews, and CTO-level guidance
                    to future-proof your platform. 由经验丰富的开发人员直接提供支持。
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🌐</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Multi-Tenant SaaS</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Building a platform that hosts multiple businesses under one roof? Multi-tenancy is tricky af if
                    done wrong.
                    Мы используем проверенные паттерны и современные библиотеки для изоляции данных и масштабируемости.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🛠️</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">DevOps Automation</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Build pipelines, deploy zero-downtime updates, auto-scale your services.
                    Manual FTP uploads are dead, fam. CICD (Continuous Integration/Continuous Deployment) or bust. 💥
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🧠</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">AI and Laravel™</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Machine Learning models, LLM APIs, intelligent agents? Bring the AI sauce to your <a
                        href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">Laravel</a> app without making
                    a mess. 我们可以帮助您整合OpenAI, Ollama, Langchain, 和更多。
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Highlighted Quote -->
        <blockquote class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <strong>And the best bit?</strong> Everything is built around <strong>SOLID</strong>,
                <strong>KISS</strong>, and <strong>DRY</strong> principles, meaning you’re getting a future-proof,
                easy-to-maintain codebase that your next dev team will actually thank you for. No spaghetti, no
                headaches.
            </p>
        </blockquote>

        <!-- Concluding Paragraph -->
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Let's be real: <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">Laravel™</a> is
                evolving crazy fast</strong> — and so are user expectations.
            Old-school PHP apps? 💤 Dead.
            Static HTML? Cute but nah.
            Modern apps need fast APIs, slick UX, real-time updates, and auto-scaling infra.
            И если вы выберете нас, то получите больше, чем просто кодеров — получите партнеров по росту. 🚀
        </p>

    </div>

    <Proposal/>

    <Cases/>

    <Footer/>

</MainLayout>


